[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    81[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   3. **The FDA-strategy artifact is a regulatory-counsel-reviewed versioned asset.** The architecture should specify the per-version regulatory-counsel sign-off, the per-version review against the bot's current scope and claims (changes to scope or claims trigger regulatory-counsel re-review), the per-version-stamping on every support-decision-record where the artifact is implicated, and the change-management process owned jointly by regulatory and behavioral-health clinical leadership.
